texts.text: *Roar*
No...
Deal with the Devil Downloader first. They're too strong.
Keep switching between your demons and weapons!
Fire all at once!
Orcus!
I shall take thee to the abyss...
>Orcus absorbs every single attack.
Don't just attack from the front! Flank it!
Devil Download...

*Snicker*
My turn!

*Wince*
It's an ambush!
(30 of Homunculus Type G left and 12 of Type J...)
(Looks like I can only control five at once. The rest can go on autopilot.)
Shell them with spirit-piercing rounds!
>The Brotherhood of Harmony launches multiple high-explosive rounds into the air.
Shield!
>A wall of light protects Alternate Hero from the barrage.
>The barrier quickly begins to crack and flake away.
(I'm sorry, my friends...)
(I'll be joining you soon.)
Just let me use the rest of my Armament and Homunculi first.
Get everybody here! Form ranks!
>More reinforcements arrive...
Okay then. That's more than I was expecting to fight.
I guess this is it. At least I got them the time they need.
Time for this former baddie to go out with a bang!
Attack...
No!
Gah!
Clumping up like that on flat ground was a big mistake.
Let hell rain from above! Fire at will!
You guys...?
No, we're surrounded! Mow them all down!
Yo, we got the upper hand thanks to our little Hero.
Megakin! What are you doing here?!
I said I don't know how long your Demonite will last...
If you don't deal with Amane Misaki now, I won't be able to help you...
This fate of this world lies in your hands, Neo Liberators.
You mean "our" hands?
Yo, we're "all" the Neo Liberators.
Let's do this, y'all! No mercy!
